This repository contains scripts for releasing DokuWiki versions.

Normal release process:

  * merge stable into old-stable

  * run php code_changes.php rcCodename
  * go into ./dokuwiki
    * check everything // FIXME: how?
    * git push && git push --tags
  * run build.sh
  * upload

  * run php code_changes.php rc2Codename
  * …

  * run php code_changes.php Codename
  * …
